    "collapsible_content_GT3bqd": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_CXXzFY": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the maximum suction power of the Honiture G20 Pro?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Honiture G20 Pro provides super strong suction power of up to 4500Pa and supports three-in-one functions of sweeping, vacuuming and mopping.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RCGpCR": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What kind of navigation does the Honiture G20 Pro use, and how does it plan its cleaning path?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The G20 Pro features Gyroscope Navigation, which follows an efficient zigzag path during cleaning, ensuring a thorough and systematic cleaning of the coverage area, minimizing missed areas.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwCEaX": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the honiture G20 pro support smart control? What are the control methods?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes, the G20 Pro supports multiple smart control methods, including:<\/p><ul><li>App control (Honysmart App): for scheduling cleaning times and switching modes.<\/li><li>Voice control: supports smart voice assistants like Alexa.<\/li><li>Remote control and on-body buttons: provide convenient physical control options.<\/li><\/ul>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_VwMC8R": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does the Honiture G20 Pro handle carpeted areas and setting \"no-go zones\"?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The G20 Pro features Carpet Auto-Boost, which automatically maximizes suction power when carpet is detected for a deep clean. The G20 Pro uses Magnetic Strip Virtual Boundaries to easily define areas that don't need to be cleaned, without having to use the app.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_wqrYY3": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are the maximum battery life and cleaning modes of the Honiture G20 Pro?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The G20 Pro features a 3200mAh lithium-ion battery with a runtime of up to 180 minutes (3 hours), making it ideal for larger homes. It supports four cleaning modes: automatic, spot cleaning, edge cleaning, and scheduled cleaning.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        }
      },
